    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>+ In nomine domini Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi Dei eterni <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3002"
                            >Iordanus</persName> divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>. Peticioni dilecti sui clementer favet.
                        Notum sit omnibus Sancte Catholice Ecclesie filiis me quem ad hoc divina
                        gratia promovit in principem ut ecclesiarum defensorem et eorum que
                        perdiderint, restitutor existam,<rs key="#Intercessory"> interveniente</rs>
                        itaque <persName key="#Principissa #marriage" ref="#people/3011"
                            >Gaitelgrima</persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">uxore</rs> mea sagacissima <rs key="#Principissa"
                            >principissa</rs>, concessisse et confirmasse <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3041">domini
                            Salvatoris</orgName> constructo in <placeName ref="#places/4066">insula
                            Maris</placeName> in pertinentia <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/2350">Neapolis</placeName> et tibi domino <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/3055">Urso</persName> eiusdem
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">reverendissimo</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>, videlicet: <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3074">Sancti Nicolai de Surrento</orgName> cum
                        omnibus suis pertinentiis et cum omnibus pertinentiis prescripti domini
                        Salvatoris eiusdem ecclesie subiectis et quic quid pertinet prescripto
                        monasterio in tota pertinetia <placeName ref="#places/2861" key="#Cities"
                            >Surrenti</placeName>, et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >omnes terras</rs> prefato monasterio pertinentes infra <rs key="#Fines"
                            >fines</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villages/settlements #Fines" ref="#places/4012"><geogName
                                ref="#estates/3037">Lauri</geogName></placeName> et <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3075">Sancti Felicis de Nola</orgName> et <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3076">Sancti Nicandri</orgName> cum omnibus
                        eorum pertinentiis que in <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/4003" key="#Cities"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/3038">Acerre</geogName></placeName> esse videntur cum
                            <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et cum omnibus suis aliis pertinentiis et cum <rs
                            key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs>, quos ibi habetis et cum ….. etate
                        ….. hominibus quos in eadem ecclesia eodemque loco monasterii acquirent, nec
                        non et confirmamus prefato monasterio eiusque abbati <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3023">Sancte Marie de Casolla</orgName> cum
                        omnibus territoriis et pertinentiis, quas ibi prefatum monasterium domini
                        Salvatoris modo possidet et quas in antea acquisiverit, nec non et
                        confirmamus prefato monasterio eiusque abbati ecclesiam Sancte Marie de
                        Casolla cum omnibus territoriis et pertinentiis, quas ibi prefatum
                        monasterium domini Salvatoris modo possidet et quas in antea acquirens
                        possessurum est et <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Coloni/tenants #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3738">Sancti Salvatoris de loco
                            Feczata</orgName> cum <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> et
                        omnibus suis pertinenciis et quicquid invenitur pertinens prescripto
                        monasterio domini Salvatoris in area dominica et quicquid pertinet eidem
                        monasterio in <placeName ref="#places/4787">Saviniano</placeName> et quantum
                        pertinet eidem monasterio in loco <placeName ref="#places/5482"
                            >Ysele</placeName> et quicquid pertinet eidem sancto monasterio in <rs
                            key="#Villas">villa</rs> que dicitur <placeName ref="#places/4788"
                            key="#Villas"><geogName ref="#estates/3039"
                            >Pastoranu</geogName></placeName> et <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3077"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            >Sancti Petri de Cintoria</orgName> cum omnibus suis pertinentiis et cum
                        toto <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >campo</rs> qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#places/5483"><geogName
                                key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive"
                                ref="#estates/3040">Campanianus</geogName></placeName>. Concedimus
                        etiam prescripto monasterio Sancti Salvatoris et prefato abbati <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">omnes terras</rs> quas <persName
                            ref="#people/3031">Rannulfus de Argentia</persName> eidem monasterio
                        obtulit simul et confirmamus ibidem <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3078">Sancti Nicalay ubi dicitur
                            Trispeoli</orgName> infra pertinentias <placeName ref="#places/5008"
                            >Poteoli</placeName> et quicquid intus et foris Putheolim pertinet
                        suprascripto monasterio Sancti Salvatoris et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3079">Sancti Salvatoris que dicitur monasterium
                            Marinum ad Bale</orgName> cum suis pertinentiis et <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >silvas</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras</rs> que prefato monasterio pertinent infra <rs key="#Fines"
                            >fines</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Landed_possessions #Forests #Fines" ref="#places/2356"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/3041">Cume</geogName></placeName> et
                        concedimus ibidem <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3080">Sancti Antonii
                        </orgName>cum omnibus suis pertinentiis, quod situm esse videtur in loco
                            <placeName ref="#places/5484" key="#Villages/settlements"
                            >Posilipu</placeName> nec non et confirmamus ibidem quicquid vos
                        possidetis in <rs key="#Islands">insula</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/4081" key="#Islands">Iscle Maioris</placeName>,
                        omnes prescriptas ecclesias et terras et earum eclesiarum pertinentias,
                        concedimus et confirmamus suprascripto monasterio Sancti Salvatoris suisque
                        rectoribus et custodibus in perpetuum et nominatas reconfirmamus in eodem
                        monasterio prefatoque abbati suisque successoribus ob melius observandum
                        ecclesiam Sancti Nicandri superius scriptam et <rs key="#Villas">villam</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">homines</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terras</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Forests #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">silvas</rs> et
                        medietatem <rs key="#Riverbed">alvei</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers #Riverbed" ref="#places/2865">lanei</placeName>
                        qualiter modo possidet et qualiter acquirendo monasterium eius qui rectores
                        possessuri sunt, remoto omni contrario vel molestia omnium vicecomitum,
                        castaldeorum et omnium mortalium. Quod siquis diabolico instintu compulsus,
                        monasterium eiusque rectores de prescriptis concessionibus violare,
                        molestare, aliquodque contrarii inferre pressumpserit <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >centum libras auri obtimi</rs> persolvat, medietatem nostro palatio et
                        medietatem prefato monasterio et predicto domino abbate et soluta pena hec
                        nostra concessio et confimatio firma et inviolabilis permaneat in perpetuum.
                        Et ut firmius credatur et diligentius observentur manu nostra propria
                        subscripsimus et nostri sigilli impressione iussimus sigillari. Signum
                        domini Iordani (M) <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs>
                        principis. Ex iussione prephate serenissime potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3005">Cansolinus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> in anno principatus ipsius vicesimo quinto et
                        vicesimo anno <rs key="#Marquis/duke #Marca/ducatum">ducatus</rs> eius
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/2343"><geogName
                                key="#Marca/ducatum" ref="#estates/3001"
                            >Caserte</geogName></placeName>. Datum in kalendis aprelis, anno ab
                        incarnatione domini nostri Iesu Christi M octoagesimo tertio. Scriptum
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capue</placeName> per sextam
                        indictionem (S).</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
